casebody.data:
Andre L. WHITE, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
The STATE of Florida, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-1684 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 19, 2017 ROTHENBERG, C.J., and LAGOA and SCALES, JJ., concur.

Following review of the petition for habeas corpus relief, and the response and reply thereto, it is ordered that said petition is hereby dismissed as unauthorized.
